lead_paragraph: Ariya Jutanugarn chipped in for birdie on the final hole Friday for a 6-under 66 and a share of the lead in the TOTO Japan Classic, the LPGA Tour's first tournament in the Tokyo area since 1991.

headline.print_headline: Ariya Jutanugarn Chips In for Share of LPGA Lead in Japan
